subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Despite only leading 19 laps, Kasey Kahne won the rain-shortened 3M Performance 400 for his fourth Nextel Cup victory of the season.
snippet: Despite only leading 19 laps, Kasey Kahne won the rain-shortened 3M Performance 400 for his fourth Nextel Cup victory of the season.
